Summary: A Group of Dark Dots moving fast across the evening sky.
divs: Sighting DetailsAt 18:12GMT I was looking up at the sky to see what type of weather was approaching, I then observed about 10 possibly more grey dots at vaious levels moving rapidly in an East to Westerly direction. Using my binoculars I could see dark grey dots and had a job keeping track of them as they were moving quite fast. The conditions were bright overcast and the dots were below the clouds. The speed of the objects attracted my attention. Apart from possibly being military jets, I have no idea what these might of been. Certainly not birds. Regards, Mike
